<h3>Endpoint</h3>
<pre><code>POST /api/translate</pre></code>

<h3>Params</h3>
<pre><code class="hljs javascript">{
    "to": "Japanese",
    "from": "English", // optional
    "query": "Hello, World!"
}</pre></code>

<br><br>

<h3>Example <small>(using request-promise)</small></h3>
<pre><code class="hljs javascript">await request({
    method: "POST",
    headers: { "Authorization": "token" },
    uri: "https://api.kurisubrooks.com/api/translate",
    json: true,
    body: {
        to: "Japanese",
        query: "Hello, World!"
    }
});</pre></code>

<h3>Response</h3>
<pre><code class="hljs javascript">{
    "ok": true,
    "to": {
        "name": "Japanese",
        "local": "日本語",
        "code": "ja"
    },
    "from": {
        "name": "English",
        "local": "English",
        "code": "en"
    },
    "query": "Hello, World!",
    "result": "こんにちは、世界！"
}</code></pre>
